'''安卡拉－伊斯坦堡高速鐵路'''（{{lang-tr|'''Ankara-İstanbul hızlı tren hattı'''}}）是一條位於[[土耳其|土耳其]][[安卡拉|安卡拉]]與{{link-en|彭迪克|Pendik}}長533公里的[[高速鐵路|高速鐵路]]，全線於2019年3月通車。

==歷史==
{{see also|安卡拉－伊斯坦堡鐵路}}
[[File:Rail_transport_map_of_Turkey.png|thumb]]
路線的建設分為兩期。第一期為[[辛詹|辛詹]]至[[埃斯基謝希爾|埃斯基謝希爾]]之間合共251公里，花費7.47億美元，自2003年起開工，2007年完工並於2009年3月13日啟用。<ref name=rt>{{cite web|title=Ankara-Istanbul High-Speed Train Project, Turkey|url=http://www.railway-technology.com/projects/ankara-istanbul/|publisher=Railway Technology|accessdate=19 December 2011|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/643icguJd?url=http://www.railway-technology.com/projects/ankara-istanbul/|archivedate=2011-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Turkey's First High-Speed Train Service to Begin Next Month|url=http://www.turkishweekly.net/news/65345/turkey-39-s-first-high-speed-train-service-to-begin-next-month-.html|publisher=Turkish Weekly|accessdate=19 December 2011|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/643jOaxgC?url=http://www.turkishweekly.net/news/65345/turkey-39-s-first-high-speed-train-service-to-begin-next-month-.html|archivedate=2011-12-19|date=25 February 2009|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第二期為[[埃斯基謝希爾|埃斯基謝希爾]]至{{link-en|彭迪克|Pendik}}全長214公里，花費22.7億美元<ref name="rt"/>。費用偏高的原因是地形比第一期更具挑戰性，需要建設33條大橋及39條隧道。此期由時任土耳其總理[[埃爾多安|埃爾多安]]於2014年7月25日宣佈開通，來往安卡拉至彭迪克需時3.5小時，每日發車6對。<ref>Uysal, Onur. [http://railturkey.org/2014/08/09/istanbul-ankara-high-speed-train-new-schedule/ "New Schedule for Istanbul-Ankara High Speed Train"] {{Wayback|url=http://railturkey.org/2014/08/09/istanbul-ankara-high-speed-train-new-schedule/ |date=20201129051904 }}, ''Rail Turkey'', 9 August 2014</ref>路線會繼續向[[馬爾馬拉鐵路|馬爾馬拉鐵路]]延長。<ref>Uysal, Onur. [http://railturkey.org/2014/10/22/access-to-high-speed-train-istanbul/ "How to Get to High Speed Train in Istanbul?"] {{Wayback|url=http://railturkey.org/2014/10/22/access-to-high-speed-train-istanbul/ |date=20210116205352 }}, ''Rail Turkey'', 22 October 2014</ref>路線計劃於2016年全線開通，總花費88億[[新土耳其里拉|新土耳其里拉]]。<ref>Uysal, Onur.[http://railturkey.org/2014/01/30/high-speed-projects-need-5-billion/ "5 Billion Needed Annually for High Speed Trains"] {{Wayback|url=http://railturkey.org/2014/01/30/high-speed-projects-need-5-billion/ |date=20201027173128 }}, ''Rail Turkey'', 30 Jan 2014</ref> 

该项目所需贷款中，12.5億歐元來自[[歐洲投資銀行|歐洲投資銀行]]，1.2億歐元來自[[歐盟|歐盟]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=EIB loans €400m for Istanbul-Ankara high speed rail line|url=http://www.rail.co/2011/12/19/eib-loans-e400m-for-istanbul-ankara-high-speed-rail-line/|publisher=Rail.co|accessdate=20 December 2011|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/643kQBh0i?url=http://www.rail.co/2011/12/19/eib-loans-e400m-for-istanbul-ankara-high-speed-rail-line/|archivedate=2011-12-20|date=19 December 2011|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

[[中國鐵建|中國鐵建]]及[[中国机械进出口（集团）有限公司|中国机械进出口（集团）有限公司]]於2005年與兩間土耳其公司聯合中標建設此線。此項計劃有7.5億美元由中國借出的貸款。

